# Task 4 - Predicting Insurance Claim Amounts

## Objective
To predict medical insurance charges using customer information.

## Tools Used
Python, Pandas, Matplotlib, Seaborn, Scikit-learn

## Approach
Explored the dataset, visualized age, BMI, and smoking effects, trained a Linear Regression model, and evaluated it.

## Results
The model estimated charges and showed that smoking status strongly affects insurance costs.

## Insights
Smoking, age, and BMI are important factors in insurance charge prediction.
